text: The 2005 Dunlop British Open Championships was held at the National Squash Centre from 9–17 October 2005. Anthony Ricketts won the title defeating James Willstrop in the final. ==Seeds== ==Draw and results== ===Main draw=== ==References== Category:Men's British Open Squash Championships Category:Squash in England Men's British Open Men's British Open Squash Championship Men's British Open Squash Championship Category:2000s in Manchester Category:Sports competitions in Manchester
